      • newDelivery

        public void newDelivery(Delivery delivery)
                 throws java.util.ConcurrentModificationException
        Creates a new delivery and stores it in the delivery store of the company. The order that shall be delivered is taken off of the order store.
        Parameters:
        delivery - Object of type Delivery.
        Throws:
        java.util.ConcurrentModificationException - The passed delivery should not be tighten up is any way to an Iterator, otherwise it will throw a ConcurrentModificationException due to the delete
